Resets this co-location group, meaning that future calls to {@link #getLocationConstraint(int)}_will give out new CoLocationConstraints.__

This method can only be called when no tasks from any of the CoLocationConstraints are_executed any more.
codeText: public void resetConstraints() {_		for (CoLocationConstraint c : this.constraints) {_			if (c.isAssignedAndAlive()) {_				throw new IllegalStateException(_						"Cannot reset co-location group: some constraints still have live tasks")__			}_		}_		this.constraints.clear()__	}
